# Opus Magnum Glyph Tool

Please don't look at the code too closely, it's a giant hack. 

So basically you can use this to auto-generate base, glow and stroke glyphs for OM mods, just so you don't have to do it yourself.

To use it just run it, left-click and drag to paint in your glyph, and right-click to remove a tile.
Once you're done drawing your glyph shape, press the Export button, naturally. A window should open showing the location of the exported files, hopefully.

It currently tries to "auto-shift" the sprites you draw something that's asymmetrical, so you don't have to. If you'd like to disable this just uncheck the checkbox.

That's the whole thing so far! Feel free to use if it is useful to you too.